quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  69,38,So I swear by what you can see
  69,39,and by what you cannot see
  69,40,"this [Quran] is the speech of an honoured messenger"
  69,41,not the words of a poet- how little you believe
  69,42,nor the words of a soothsayer- how little you reflect
  69,43,"This [Quran] is a message sent down from the Lord of the Worlds"
  69,44,"if [the Prophet] had attributed some fabrication to Us"
  69,45,We would certainly have seized his right hand
  69,46,and cut off his lifeblood
  69,47,and none of you could have defended him
  69,48,"This [Quran] is a reminder for those who are aware of God"
  69,49,We know that some of you consider it to be lies
  69,50,this will be a source of bitter regret for the disbelievers
  69,51,but it is in fact the certain Truth
  69,52,"So [Prophet] glorify the name of your Lord, the Almighty"